org.apache.freemarker.core.model

Class WrappingTemplateModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.freemarker.core.model.WrappingTemplateModel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultArrayAdapter, DefaultEnumerationAdapter, DefaultIterableAdapter, DefaultIteratorAdapter, DefaultListAdapter, DefaultMapAdapter, DefaultNonListCollectionAdapter, SimpleCollection, SimpleHash, SimpleIterable, SimpleSequence

    public abstract class WrappingTemplateModel
extends Object
    Convenience base-class for containers that wrap their contained arbitrary Java objects into TemplateModel instances.
